oregon trail is a 1947 american western film directed by lesley selander and written by dorrell mcgowan and stuart e. mcgowan . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , george " gabby " hayes , russell hayden , george " gabby " hayes , russell hayden , frank mcglynn jr. , george cleveland , george cleveland , and earle hodgins . the film was released on may 1 , 1947 , by republic pictures .